Package com.fdmgroup.PCTrack.model

Class Computer

java.lang.Object
com.fdmgroup.PCTrack.model.Computer
@Entity public class Computer extends Object
One of the main objects in the software, this object registers the data of a computer into the database. It automatically designates a role based on the software that are installed on the computer.
